name: parent
description:
This work depicts parents who have experienced various directions of life, joys, sorrows and various life obstacles that have become their past journeys.
In this work, I want to convey that Life is a journey, a journey that requires high achievements on the way. Life goes on and age is increasing along with the physical body that is getting older and weaker, we can't change the past but we can change plans for the future. For that, color your life's journey more colorful and meaningful to achieve more and more valuable memories
